data.description: Beautiful 2-story house in a highly sought-after location. stunning home features 3 bedrooms, 2 and a half bathrooms, and a spacious 2-car garage. As you enter, you will be greeted by wood tile flooring in the living room and dining area, giving the space a warm and inviting feel. Kitchen boasts lots of cabinet space, perfect for storage, and a walk-in pantry for all your culinary needs. Large laundry room is equipped with built-in cabinetry and a folding countertop at a comfortable height, making chores a breeze. Gated community. The community park just across the street provides a great place for relaxation and outdoor activities. Second floor features a loft area, perfect for a home office or entertainment space. Second and third bedrooms both come with spacious walk-in closets. Good-sized backyard, great for outdoor entertaining and gardening. The house is equipped with a water softener ready system and a less than a year old water heater. With Solar Energy system.
